doctype html
html
	head
		title Password Reset
		link(
			rel='stylesheet'
			type='text/css'
			integrity='sha384-BVYiiSIFeK1dGmJRAkycuHAHRg32OmUcww7on3RYdg4Va+PmSTsz/K68vbdEjh4u'
			crossorigin='anonymous'
			href='https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css'
		)
	body
		div(class='container')
			h1 Password Reset

			p Hi there #{userFriendlyName},

			p
				| You are receiving this e-mail because a request was made to reset the password on your&nbsp;
				a(href=`${siteUrl}`) BottomTime.ca
				| &nbsp;user account. Please follow the link below within 24 hours of receiving this e-mail to
				| reset your password.

			p
				a(href=`${resetUrl}`) Reset My Password!
			
			p
				| If you&nbsp;
				strong did not
				| &nbsp;request that your password be reset and you suspect something suspicious is going on please
				| report the incident to&nbsp;
				a(href=`mailto:${supportEmail}`) #{supportEmail}
				| &nbsp;for investigation. This e-mail was generated automatically. Please do not try to reply to it.
				| Your message will not be received.

			p Cheers,
			p The BottomTime Team

			p
				small
					em Copyright &copy; Chris Carleton, 2019
